16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 25 O.S. 2021, Section 1201, as
18 amended by Section 4, Chapter 365, O.S.L. 2024 (25 O.S. Supp. 2024,
19 Section 1201), is amended to read as follows:
20 Section 1201. In Section 1101 et seq. of this title, unless the
21 context otherwise requires:
22 1. “Antisemitism”, as defined by the International Holocaust
23 Remembrance Alliance (IHRA), is a certain perception of Jews, which
24 may be expressed as hatred toward Jews. Rhetorical and physical
